---
title: "US13 — Manually enter workout details"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ManualEntryScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>StartWorkoutSession / EndWorkoutSession
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession
  A->>B: enter type, duration, metrics
  B->>C: save manual session
  C->>E: WorkoutSession with connectedDeviceId = null
  note right of E: null device marks<br/>a manual entry
  E-->>C: saved (+XP)
  C-->>B: done
  B-->>A: session appears in History
  note over E: persisted via WorkoutGateway → Supabase
